{"_id":"hans00000001","name":"Hans M\u00fcller","type":"hero","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"archetype":"Idealist","nation":"eisen","background":"Soldier","traits":{"brawn":{"value":4},"finesse":{"value":2},"resolve":{"value":3},"panache":{"value":2},"wits":{"value":1}},"skills":{"investigation":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"stealth":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theft":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"legends":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sorcery":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theology":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"aim":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"athletics":{"value":3,"specialty":true},"melee":{"value":4,"specialty":true},"sailing":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"strategy":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"survival":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"intrigue":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"protocol":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"selfControl":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"engineering":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"humanities":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"science":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"empathy":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"persuasion":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"perform":{"value":0,"specialty":false}},"combatAptitudes":{"attack":{"trait":"brawn"},"defence":{"trait":"finesse"},"damage":{"trait":"brawn"},"toughness":{"trait":"resolve"},"manoeuvre":{"trait":"brawn"}},"wounds":{"minor":0,"dramatic":[false,false,false,false],"helpless":false},"heroPoints":1,"biography":"<p>Eisen bodyguard hired to protect Hugues. Learned a brutal lesson: death never warns you. Joined Los Vagabundos because the idea that one could kill 'to save souls' is unbearable to him.</p><p><strong>Advantages:</strong> Dracheneisen Panzerfaust, Idealist, Duelist Academy (Mauer aus Eisen), Perfect Balance, I Won't Die Here, Foolhardy, Passionate, Soldier</p>","notes":""},"items":[{"_id":"lQML6GzSQpIxRPCI","name":"Dracheneisen Panzerfaust","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You own a masterwork weapon, a dracheneisen panzerfaust forged by one of the last Nibelungen. You gain 1 additional dice on any roll where you use it.</p>","key":"","scope":"skill","scopeSkills":["melee"],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HAnjsBdr06AqcMUH","name":"Idealist","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You gain 1 additional die on any roll meant to directly protect someone.</p>","key":"","scope":"always","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"LhMAN45kZy3bw1rx","name":"Duelist Academy (Mauer aus Eisen)","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Hans was trained at the Eisenfaust Academy. When he successfully parries an Attack, he may spend 1 Hero Point to trap his opponent's blade with his Panzerfaust: their Attack and Defence Aptitudes are reduced by 1 for their next turn.</p>","key":"idealist-parry","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"AeSaOP5sww7XFoez","name":"Perfect Balance","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend a Hero Point to cross a narrow beam, leap from one place to another, or perform any other feat based on balance and agility.</p>","key":"","scope":"skill","scopeSkills":["athletics"],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"05bDnVGII8koflsr","name":"I Won't Die Here","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend 1 Hero Point to ignore all negative effects (Dramatic Wounds, Threats, etc.) for 1 round. The Hero point must be spent before the roll.</p>","key":"wont-die-here","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"EMVNSEoxYsi91Mbp","name":"Foolhardy","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, you gain 1 Hero Point when your recklessness, nerve, or audacity gets you into trouble.</p>","key":"foolhardy","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"NBBHPvWm3tx6LOjW","name":"Passionate","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, cancel all Wounds suffered by another character. Instead, you suffer one Dramatic Wound.</p>","key":"passionate","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"aTj9TmvuCefYKojI","name":"Soldier","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, you may \u201chold your line.\u201d Choose a semi-enclosed area. As long as you don't move, and until the end of the Scene, no enemy can pass through that area without first going through you and facing you.</p>","key":"soldier","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hugues0000001","name":"Hugues de la Chapelle Montmoront","type":"hero","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"archetype":"Schemer","nation":"montaigne","background":"Politician","traits":{"brawn":{"value":1},"finesse":{"value":2},"resolve":{"value":2},"panache":{"value":4},"wits":{"value":3}},"skills":{"investigation":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"stealth":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"theft":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"legends":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sorcery":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theology":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"aim":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"athletics":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"melee":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"sailing":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"strategy":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"survival":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"intrigue":{"value":4,"specialty":true},"protocol":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"selfControl":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"engineering":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"humanities":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"science":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"empathy":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"persuasion":{"value":4,"specialty":false},"perform":{"value":2,"specialty":false}},"combatAptitudes":{"attack":{"trait":"finesse"},"defence":{"trait":"panache"},"damage":{"trait":"wits"},"toughness":{"trait":"resolve"},"manoeuvre":{"trait":"panache"}},"wounds":{"minor":0,"dramatic":[false,false,false,false],"helpless":false},"heroPoints":1,"biography":"<p>Montaigne diplomat and Vagabundo. Smiles, bows, and quotes protocol, but knows the slightest misstep could spark a crisis. Joined Los Vagabundos to act for the greater good from inside the highest circles.</p><p><strong>Advantages:</strong> Reputation (Upright), Schemer, Staredown, Friend at Court, Indomitable Will, Intuitive, Politician, Relentless</p>","notes":""},"items":[{"_id":"3xSODYjftjBwH4Dj","name":"Reputation: Upright","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You gain 1 additional die on rolls when your Reputation works in your favor.</p>","key":"","scope":"always","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"Yz5dNhmjDWKuHrIF","name":"Schemer","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You gain 1 additional die on Politics Skills to find information in a court or at a social event.</p>","key":"","scope":"skill","scopeSkills":["intrigue","protocol","selfControl"],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"Z9SWBMNub2vkfvm1","name":"Staredown","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You gain 1 additional die when you try to intimidate or persuade through fear.</p>","key":"","scope":"skill","scopeSkills":["persuasion"],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"CL9MNWsyF29f5tPi","name":"Friend at Court","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend 1 Hero Point to reveal that you have a close friend present at a party, ball, or any other social event.</p>","key":"friend-at-court","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"hHjwkfw6mKCBDy3Q","name":"Indomitable Will","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend 1 Hero Point to automatically resist when another character tries to intimidate, seduce, or manipulate you.</p>","key":"indomitable-will","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"luODSdrQQEcCybHD","name":"Intuitive","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, ask the Game Master a yes/no question. They must answer honestly with \u201cYes\u201d or \u201cNo\u201d.</p>","key":"intuitive","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"ReJkj6AjiyTPTglZ","name":"Politician","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, obtaining an audience with a decision-maker automatically succeeds.</p>","key":"politician","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"vruqjGp5ppfKuR1J","name":"Relentless","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, you gain 1 Hero Point when you refuse to settle for a merely \u201csatisfactory\u201d result or a small victory, and it gets you into trouble.</p>","key":"relentless","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mallory000001","name":"Mallory Reilly","type":"hero","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"archetype":"Outlaw","nation":"avalon","background":"Criminal","traits":{"brawn":{"value":2},"finesse":{"value":4},"resolve":{"value":2},"panache":{"value":2},"wits":{"value":2}},"skills":{"investigation":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"stealth":{"value":3,"specialty":true},"theft":{"value":4,"specialty":true},"legends":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sorcery":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theology":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"aim":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"athletics":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"melee":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"sailing":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"strategy":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"survival":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"intrigue":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"protocol":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"selfControl":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"engineering":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"humanities":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"science":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"empathy":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"persuasion":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"perform":{"value":0,"specialty":false}},"combatAptitudes":{"attack":{"trait":"finesse"},"defence":{"trait":"finesse"},"damage":{"trait":"finesse"},"toughness":{"trait":"resolve"},"manoeuvre":{"trait":"finesse"}},"wounds":{"minor":0,"dramatic":[false,false,false,false],"helpless":false},"heroPoints":1,"biography":"<p>High-end art thief from Avalon. Under the identity of an impeccable Avalonian steward, operates from the shadows. Los Vagabundos recruited Mallory for their talent at blending into crowds and getting into places they aren't welcome.</p><p><strong>Advantages:</strong> Cast Iron Stomach, Outlaw, Small, Brush Pass, Got it!, Second Story Work, Criminal, Envious, Fortunate</p>","notes":""},"items":[{"_id":"zB9wxAnYkFNca4rm","name":"Cast Iron Stomach","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"passive","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Drink as much as you like; alcohol has no effect on you. You suffer no negative consequences.</p>","key":"cast-iron-stomach","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"6JyAh15YECejgC3j","name":"Outlaw","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You gain 1 additional die on Cunning Skills to disappear into crowds and across rooftops.</p>","key":"","scope":"skill","scopeSkills":["investigation","stealth","theft"],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"C4kcY4GWilfPfRKO","name":"Small","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You gain 1 additional die on any roll where your size is an advantage.</p>","key":"","scope":"always","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"Wfu39KoQGEi5ANlZ","name":"Brush Pass","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend 1 Hero Point to cut a purse, slip a ring off someone\u2019s finger, or plant an object that fits in your hand on another character without them noticing.</p>","key":"brush-pass","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"lescX2piVv9frtKF","name":"Got it!","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend 1 Hero Point to instantly pick a lock, open a safe, or disarm a trap.</p>","key":"got-it","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"GyQy3KTFnS9PqaWa","name":"Second Story Work","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend 1 Hero Point to find a way to access a building, room, or guarded site without being noticed. Spend 1 additional Hero Point to bring someone with you.</p>","key":"second-story-work","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"vrTn2K8neiNz4CRh","name":"Criminal","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, spotting the best exit or hiding place automatically succeeds.</p>","key":"criminal","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"sFxAiB8Ec2U7aroN","name":"Envious","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, you gain 1 Hero Point when you try to take something you covet, and it gets you into trouble.</p>","key":"envious","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"BURdEcfZNyAn4sbg","name":"Fortunate","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, reroll all or part of a dice roll.</p>","key":"fortunate","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"manuela000001","name":"Manuela de Olivera de la Cruz","type":"hero","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"archetype":"Cursed Heir","nation":"castille","background":"Officer","traits":{"brawn":{"value":2},"finesse":{"value":2},"resolve":{"value":3},"panache":{"value":2},"wits":{"value":3}},"skills":{"investigation":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"stealth":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theft":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"legends":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sorcery":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"theology":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"aim":{"value":2,"specialty":true},"athletics":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"melee":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"sailing":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"strategy":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"survival":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"intrigue":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"protocol":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"selfControl":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"engineering":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"humanities":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"science":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"empathy":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"persuasion":{"value":1,"specialty":false},"perform":{"value":0,"specialty":false}},"combatAptitudes":{"attack":{"trait":"finesse"},"defence":{"trait":"wits"},"damage":{"trait":"resolve"},"toughness":{"trait":"brawn"},"manoeuvre":{"trait":"resolve"}},"wounds":{"minor":0,"dramatic":[false,false,false,false],"helpless":false},"heroPoints":1,"biography":"<p>Castillian army officer and member of Los Vagabundos. Her father is a Villain allied with the worst scoundrels. She seeks to prove she is not doomed by blood to follow his path.</p><p><strong>Advantages:</strong> Firearms Specialist, Team Player, Cursed Heir, Leadership, Camaraderie, Altruistic, Officer, Unfortunate</p>","notes":""},"items":[{"_id":"c0LkZN2gPLezr5yS","name":"Firearms Specialist","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"passive","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You gain a Specialty in Aim when using a firearm. When you make a roll using this Skill, dice \u201cexplode\u201d on a result of 9 or 10.</p>","key":"firearms-specialist","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"qmKyp4YHOkm3M0Zr","name":"Team Player","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"passive","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>When you spend 1 Hero Point to help another Hero, they add 4d10 to their hand (instead of 3d10).</p>","key":"team-player","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"YLK2wIqxRGxHHuJr","name":"Cursed Heir","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>By invoking your family lineage (villain), you gain 1 additional die on Politics Skills to gain access to discussions / secret meetings.</p>","key":"","scope":"skill","scopeSkills":["intrigue","protocol","selfControl"],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"V0iIO9f2zhASCPUT","name":"Leadership","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You gain 1 additional die on any roll meant to spur a group into action or coordinate collective actions.</p>","key":"","scope":"always","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"NQMnszHlTnTIrYQx","name":"Camaraderie","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You may spend your Hero Points for your allies (outside of Helping Hand, for example, to increase Damage). This requires that you be in a position to help them, at minimum, present in the same room.</p>","key":"camaraderie","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"j6AaSjZnB16L7SHU","name":"Altruistic","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, you may suffer a harmful effect (such as Wounds or a penalty) in place of another character.</p>","key":"altruistic","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"UvZVuGdZ34fFqSjl","name":"Officer","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, Manuela cuts through the chaos with a brief order: she may automatically end a state of fear, panic, or disorganization. The affected allies may act normally from this turn onward.</p>","key":"officer","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"0mw8NFd00XRAW5fE","name":"Unfortunate","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, you gain 1 additional Hero Point when you choose to fail an important roll without even rolling the dice.</p>","key":"unfortunate","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"veronica00001","name":"Veronica Cardinale","type":"hero","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"archetype":"Conspirator","nation":"vodacce","background":"Sorte Strega","traits":{"brawn":{"value":2},"finesse":{"value":2},"resolve":{"value":2},"panache":{"value":3},"wits":{"value":3}},"skills":{"investigation":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"stealth":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"theft":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"legends":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sorcery":{"value":3,"specialty":true},"theology":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"aim":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"athletics":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"melee":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"sailing":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"strategy":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"survival":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"intrigue":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"protocol":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"selfControl":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"engineering":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"humanities":{"value":2,"specialty":false},"science":{"value":0,"specialty":false},"empathy":{"value":4,"specialty":true},"persuasion":{"value":3,"specialty":false},"perform":{"value":0,"specialty":false}},"combatAptitudes":{"attack":{"trait":"panache"},"defence":{"trait":"wits"},"damage":{"trait":"panache"},"toughness":{"trait":"resolve"},"manoeuvre":{"trait":"panache"}},"wounds":{"minor":0,"dramatic":[false,false,false,false],"helpless":false},"heroPoints":1,"biography":"<p>Vodacce Sorte Strega and widow. Carefully smothered every sign of sorcery to avoid being promised to a prince-merchant. Joined Los Vagabundos because their cause spoke to her: striking the powerful by using their secrets as weapons.</p><p><strong>Advantages:</strong> Sorcery (Sorte Strega), Conspirator, Barterer, Extended Family, Oath, Curious, Illuminating, Sorte Strega (once per game Force Fate free)</p><p><em>Note: Add a Sorte Strega sorcery Item to this character to enable the sorcery tab.</em></p>","notes":""},"items":[{"_id":"EclvXp8We9OOt7FZ","name":"Sorcery","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"passive","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You are a Sorte Strega and know how to read the threads of Destiny. Handled by the Sorcery tab (Reading/Weaving, Backlash).</p>","key":"sorcery","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"wmq22zTGvdDJN9UB","name":"Conspirator","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"situational","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>You gain 1 additional die on Cunning Skills when your plans were prepared in advance.</p>","key":"","scope":"skill","scopeSkills":["investigation","stealth","theft"],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"dL2KXs7L4DBVbvZB","name":"Barterer","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend 1 Hero Point to persuade someone to accept a deal. The Game Master may spend 1 Villainy point to make a Villain immune to this effect.</p>","key":"barterer","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"UdkHo7q4ThWPbFQW","name":"Extended Family","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend 1 Hero Point to discover that a distant cousin is nearby. They can provide shelter, gear, or information.</p>","key":"extended-family","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"GHUum4l972QQcI18","name":"Oath","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"heroic","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Spend as many Hero Points as you wish and make a promise to another character. For the rest of the Scene, when you take an Action aimed at keeping that promise, add 1 additional die to your hand per Hero Point invested.</p>","key":"oath","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":0,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"4n7f7kB4uymNIWg7","name":"Curious","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, you gain 1 Hero Point when you take an interest in something, and it gets you into trouble.</p>","key":"curious","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"nEDhg7pTDO0q6Ezp","name":"Illuminating","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, you can tell whether someone is lying to you.</p>","key":"illuminating","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}},{"_id":"0sUqJJTvLK8es4kB","name":"Sorte Strega","type":"advantage","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"category":"extraordinary","hpCost":1,"used":false,"description":"<p>Once per game, you may Force Fate for free, i.e., obtain a Success without the Game Master gaining Villainy points.</p>","key":"sorte-strega-force-fate","scope":"none","scopeSkills":[],"scopeTrait":"","bonusDice":1,"usesMax":1,"usesSpent":0,"active":false,"activeValue":0,"activeNote":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
